@SimCenter.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5284

### 회원가입
POST {{SimCenter.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "driver@simcenter.test",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!",
  "displayName": "홍길동"
}

### 로그인 (accessToken 획득)
POST {{SimCenter.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "driver@simcenter.test",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

### 내 프로필 (위 로그인 응답의 accessToken을 붙여넣기)
GET {{SimCenter.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/me
Authorization: Bearer <accessToken>

